Class Worker

java.lang.Object
  nnsec.server.Worker
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.rmi.Remote, java.rmi.server.Unreferenced, WorkerIFace
public class Worker
extends java.lang.Object
implements WorkerIFace, java.rmi.server.Unreferenced

This class implements the related interface to turn himself into a remote class, so that clients can ask for a remote instance of Worker.
